{"tid":2112450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍雙航母戰鬥群 本月以來進行第二度南海軍演","createTime":"2020-07-17T10:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T11:06:21.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee2132a442e3eda0ec7768736ce7430fd5e40e0","tid":2112450,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"美軍雙航母戰鬥群恢復在南海軍演 國際 發佈時間 2020-07-17 16:35 最後更新時間 2020-07-17 16:35 <br />\n<br />\n南海局勢持續緊張，美國在星期一正式拒絕承認中方的南海九段線主張後，美軍兩個航空母艦戰鬥群，恢復在南海演習，是本月以來美軍第二度有爭議海域進行聯合軍演。太平洋艦隊發表聲明說，參與演習的尼米茲號及列根號航母戰鬥群，共有12000多名軍官及120多軍機。 美國國務卿蓬佩奧早前說，世界不會允許北京將南海視為它的海上帝國，美國會與東南亞盟友和夥伴一起，共同維護海上主權。中方抗議美軍的行動是推動南海軍事化，破壞南海和平穩定。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2347655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2347655&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=f463346a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2347655</a><br />\n<br />\n好嬲好嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f517703f8c2ea2676992a4ac27c611f535a664","tid":2112450,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njWMYEf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnjWMYEf.gif&h=dd39f6dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0cbea9bde0f411bbed5044ec677696f923753ac","tid":2112450,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:29:52.000Z","msg":"真係要入定黃金同糧食先"},{"pid":"65de2fca6b347bf22f6e8b361019f0c467399201","tid":2112450,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"南海係我地架 係基本法腐乳左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgm